     # Derived from solving the system:
     # 1) (M+m)x_dd + (ml cos)theta_dd = F + f_cart + ml*theta_d^2*sin
     # 2) (ml cos)x_dd + (ml^2)theta_dd = mgl sin + f_joint
 
